Package: PatientLevelPrediction
Type: Package
Title: Developing patient level prediction using data in the OMOP Common Data
    Model
Version: 6.3.9.9999
Date: 2024-10-10
Authors@R: c(
    person("Egill", "Fridgeirsson", email = "e.fridgeirsson@erasmusmc.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
